<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_491" id="245r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_491_r1l17">Johan <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Jung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Grafen cʒü <expan>Spanh<ex>eim</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_491_r1l18"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> vvi </del> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> nam </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_491_r1l19"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / als Jr <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> veinden getan habt / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_491_r1l20">wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / vnd ıſt vns die cʒwitracht cʒwiſchen ew vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_491_r1l21"><expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vviderſachen nicht lıeb / vnd <expan>vvolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / daʒ Jr mit Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_491_r1l22"><expan>gütlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd wol eynig wert / . vnd vvo wir des rede hören </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_491_r1l23">ſo wöllen wir ewr gnad <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>verantwurt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſo wir peſt mügen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_491_r1l24">wan wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lıeb vnd dinſt <expan>beweiſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_491_r1l25">Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııj̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Margarethe / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_491" id="245r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Johan <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>jung<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, grafen czü <expan>Spanh<ex>eim</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r,</expan> als ir uns
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> nam <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan> als
                        ir <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> veinden getan habt,
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> und ist uns die czwitracht
                        czwischen ew und <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> widersachen nicht lieb und
                                <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>, daz ir mit in
                            <expan>gütliche<ex>n</ex></expan> und wol eynig wert. Und wo wir des
                        rede hören, so wöllen wir ewr gnad <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>verantwurt<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> so wir pest mügen; wan wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lieb und dinst
                            <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Margarethe.
                    </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
